01:08:25,601 --> 01:08:26,811
Open up!

785
01:08:27,311 --> 01:08:28,521
Get in.

786
01:08:30,064 --> 01:08:31,023
Go!

787
01:08:37,822 --> 01:08:38,948
Abbas.

788
01:08:45,579 --> 01:08:46,914
Abbas.

789
01:08:46,997 --> 01:08:48,124
Abbas!

790
01:08:51,669 --> 01:08:53,003
Abbas.

791
